---
title: Golden Halloumi and  Bacon Sandwiches with Caramelized Onions, Potato Wedges and Smoky Aioli
description: Tonight, serve up a hearty meat-free sandwich made with a 'patty' of golden breaded halloumi! We've added smoky aioli and sweet caramelized onions to turn this easy dinner into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-de-bacon-et-dhaloumi-dore-3885280e.jpg
